<title>USA: Bell Microproducts Inc names CFO.</title>
<headline>Bell Microproducts Inc names CFO.</headline>
<dateline>SAN JOSE, Calif. 1997-07-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bell Microproducts Inc Wednesday appointed Bruce Jaffe as chief financial officer.</p>
<p>Jaffe was formerly president and chief operating officer of Bell Industries, where he worked for 29 years.</p>
<p>Jaffe replaces Remo Canessa, vice president of finance and secretary, who held the position on an interim basis since the retirement of the previous chief financial officer.</p>
